      • addCard

        public Deck addCard​(Card card)
             throws DeckIsLockedException
        Add a card to the Deck. Will throw an exception if the Deck is locked.

        Returns the deck so that it can be chained: `.addCard(...).addCard(...)`

        Parameters:
        card - Card to be added
        Returns:
        the Deck after the card has been added
        Throws:
        DeckIsLockedException - The Deck has been locked. No more modifications can be made.

      • lock

        public Deck lock()
        Locks the Deck to prevent modifications.

        This is a one-way process and cannot be reversed.

        Returns:
        the Deck
